verbose_text: Paired comparisons of each behavioral condition in each area showed that IEG expression in the Vocal Production condition was significantly less in two areas for both the Vocal Perception [RTM (p = 0.03), RM (p = 0.01)] and three areas for Antiphonal Calling [RTM (p = 0.03), RM (p = 0.01), and CM (p = 0.01)] conditions.
